srcu-cbmc: Use /usr/bin/awk instead of /bin/awk

Most OS distribution have awk in /usr/bin not in /bin
Without this patch, kernel-devsrc fails to build as
runtime dependency for srcu-cbmc script /bin/awk is
not found.

